  "text": "One of the important individual attribute that affects monetary well-being in retirement is how obvious an individual is about its after retirement goals. An analysis on about 1,500 inhabitants of New Zealand discovered that there is correlation between clarity of financial goals and financial planning of retirees [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
